title: Denise Elwood's Testimony
meta_content: Praise God! Miss Elwood was set free from fear the moment Pastor Tom prayed for her
content:
I wanted to testify to you, that last week when you prayed for me, I was delivered from a spirit of fear that was coming against me and I want to praise God for my freedom and thank you for your obedience. In His Love,
Denise Elwood
